      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1025 - It is narrated from Ishaq ibn Ammar who said:\n\"Abul Hasan al-Awwal (as) said to me: 'When you are in doubt, rely on what you are certain of.'\nI said: 'Is this a principle?'\nImam (as) said: 'Yes.'"
